<paragraph pageId="0" pageNumber="167">Remark.</paragraph>
<paragraph pageId="0" pageNumber="167">This operational taxonomic unit is known by one specimen which distinctly differs from other representatives of the genus. We consider this material unacceptable for describing a new species now but provide a diagnosis.</paragraph>
